quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  2,102,"Nde …ìe ngoppi diine Alla o …ìe njokki penaale …óe sey…óaneeji kaalata e laamu Annabiijo Alla Suleymaan kisal won e makko, …ói cikki (numi) ko mbilewu o tabintiniri laamu makko, Suleymaan yeddiraani mbilewu - wano yahuud en cikkiri - kono sey…óaneeji kam njeddii nde …ìe ngonnoo e jannginde yim…ìe …ìee mbilewu jippinanoongu dow malaykaa…ìe …ói…óo …ìe: Haaruut e Maaruut, to saare Baabel, Iraak, ngam humpitaade e √±oolde yim…ìe …ìe, kala nde malaykaa…ìe …ìe nganndini go…ó…óo mbilewu …ìe ndeentina mo la…ì…ìinana mo: minen ko min humpittoo…ìe yim…ìe …ìe, janngude ma mbilewu taa wa…óe njeddaa, wa…ói e ma…ì…ìe njanngi mbelewu seerndoowu gorko e debbo mum, aawa nga√±ngu hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, …ìeen mbilee…ìe mbaawaa lorrude hay gooto sonaa e belee…óe Alla, …ìe njannga ko lorrata …ìe tawa nafataa …ìe, …ìeen yahudee…ìe nganndii wonde kala mbo lomtini deftere Alla nde mbilewu o maletaake √±ande laakara, bone woodanii …ìe e ko …ìe lomtini sariya Alla o mbilewu, so tawiino …ìe nganndi …óum nafataa …ìe mba…óataano …óee golle bon…óe e majjere …ìanngunde."
  2,103,"Tawno yahuud en ngoon…óinii Alla e goonga, …ìe kuliri Mo rewde Mo, …ìe ngoppi woopde Mo; ndeen barke Alla …ìurata mo∆¥∆¥ande …ìe e ko …ìe ngoni ko, tawno e…ìe nganndi ko nafata …ìe."
  2,104,"Alla Toow…óo O Mbo tinndina goon…óin…ìe …ìee su…ìaade konngi mo∆¥∆¥i, O wii …ìe: onon goon…óin…ìe taa mbi'ee konngol: {aynu min}; woni: aynu ge…óe amen; sabu yahuud en na mbi'a noon Annabiijo (jkm) tawa …ìe paandii heen ko maanaa bon…óo, woni …ìurtere, Alla ha…ói ngol konngol ngam sukkude ngal damal, O yamiri jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìe yo mbi'at: {habba min}; woni: mu√±an min haa min paama ko kaalataa ko, ngol konngol na adda maanaa o tigi. Yeddu…ìe Alla …ìe lette muus…óe na ngoodani …ìe."
  2,105,"Yeddu…ìe …ìee - foti ko yim…ìe deftere wolla ko renndin…ìe e Alla - nji…óataa jooma mon jippinana on hay mo∆¥∆¥ere, foti ko see…óa maa ko heewi, Alla e yurmeende Makko heerori wa…óande annabaagu e wahyu e goon…óingol mbo O welaa e jeyaa…ìe Makko, Kanko woni Joom …ìural mawngal, alaa ko tagaa…óo da√±ata sonaa iwa e Makko, ko e …ìural Makko O neliri Nulaa…óo o, O jippini deftere nde."